{"tid":123403,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"世界新聞攝影大獎2017精選圖片","createTime":"2017-02-17T00:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T10:00:23.000Z","uid":81228,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5262d4821d5109e14219b7500fb70858f8eb84","tid":123403,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:03:02.000Z","msg":"世界新聞攝影大賽自1957年起每年一度於荷蘭舉行，至今已是第60屆。是屆大賽共有來自125個國家、5034名攝影師參加，經評判從八萬多張參賽圖片中精挑細選後，日前已經公布得獎名單。獎項包括年度圖片及八大組別，包括當代議題、日常生活、一般新聞、長期攝影計劃、自然、人物特寫、體育及焦點新聞。<br />\n<br />\n年度圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/5ca84d8b37c64ea1a103af110ed9795e.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/1380/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F5ca84d8b37c64ea1a103af110ed9795e.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F1380%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=9abca709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2016年12月19日，在土耳其的一家畫廊內，22歲的休班警員Mevl&uuml;t Mert Altıntaş射殺俄羅斯駐土耳其大使Andrey Karlov，並大聲呼喊。攝：Burhan Ozbilici<br />\n<br />\n美聯社攝影記者Burhan Ozbilici鏡頭下的俄羅斯駐土耳其大使遭槍手刺殺場面贏得今屆年度圖片。這幅極具爆炸性相片於去年12月發生後已旋即成為全球焦點，如今獲得年度圖片獎項後又惹來熱議。評委會主席Stuart Franklin針對這個結果，在《衛報》發表了一篇名為《這幅恐怖主義的影像不應成為年度圖片，我投了反對票》的文章，指出這張照片雖具影響力，但恐怕會宣揚了恐怖分子的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n以下是其餘八個類別的精選獲獎圖片：<br />\n<br />\n當代議題<br />\n<br />\n單幅一等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/ba5151fa68bd406690ee9e1073fda0c8.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2Fba5151fa68bd406690ee9e1073fda0c8.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=7bb11b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2016年7月9日，路易斯安那州的示威中，一個黑人女人兩手空空，走向防暴警察面前。攝：Jonathan Bachman<br />\n<br />\n圖輯二等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/0137ae4a4bf049c495a5540dec9d1cde.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F0137ae4a4bf049c495a5540dec9d1cde.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=352dd5e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在巴西東北部的鄉村地區裏，兩歲的Marcela望著患有由寨卡病毒引發的小頭症的雙胞胎妹妹。攝：Lalo de Almeida<br />\n<br />\n日常生活<br />\n<br />\n單幅一等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/8ebf0413a86149dcbe10454fe40a98b0.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F8ebf0413a86149dcbe10454fe40a98b0.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=87ec948d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在阿富汗首都喀布爾一間醫院，Najiba正抱著被炸彈炸傷的兩歲侄兒Shabir。攝：Paula Bronstein<br />\n<br />\n單幅二等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/db5316baf9994615aad21b51232924af.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2Fdb5316baf9994615aad21b51232924af.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=b95fb284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在中國徐州一所體操學校內，四名體操學生正在做腳趾壓力訓練。攝：Tiejun Wang<br />\n<br />\n單幅三等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/ae1736f700584bc892db00e77bde77c6.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2Fae1736f700584bc892db00e77bde77c6.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=4b2441b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從喀什開出的火車上，一名維吾爾族女士的絲襪內放了幾張紙幣。維吾爾婦女雖信奉穆斯林，但通常不會有太保守的衣著習慣。攝：Matthieu Paley<br />\n<br />\n圖輯三等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/32131e8b729c4c6e8edf479edb79c6f8.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F32131e8b729c4c6e8edf479edb79c6f8.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=60187a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「救恩島」是一個隱蔽和沉默的東正教社區，成立於20世紀90年代初。目前容納300男孩和女孩。攝：Francesco Comello<br />\n<br />\n一般新聞<br />\n<br />\n圖輯一等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/141d48f44fbe467eaa2ee440090f6f69.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F141d48f44fbe467eaa2ee440090f6f69.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=176e7fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在菲律賓馬尼拉，兩名被不明身份的男子殺害的受害者的屍體伏在街道上，他們分別為48歲的Frederick Mafe和23歲的Arjay Lumbago。有警察於現場搜集證據。攝：Daniel Berehulak<br />\n<br />\n圖輯二等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/732db886e20c49a7800d9ba36e4d53c2.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F732db886e20c49a7800d9ba36e4d53c2.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=292dfb22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2016年11月12日，在伊拉克第二大城市摩蘇爾，一個家庭正開車逃離戰火。攝：Sergey Ponomarev"},{"pid":"6849e60f7409998c9446b4f3253d3d0d482c4101","tid":123403,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:03:14.000Z","msg":"長期攝影計劃<br />\n<br />\n圖輯一等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/7697f047d02c41318cddb445f389e237.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F7697f047d02c41318cddb445f389e237.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=263dd9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在烏克蘭Luhanskaya村莊發生空襲，平民正慌忙逃離火災區。攝：Valery Melnikov<br />\n<br />\n圖輯一等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/f04fd7c91d924153b35574c45fced56e.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2Ff04fd7c91d924153b35574c45fced56e.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=f4176b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個難民家庭正坐巴士經過邊境驛站。自2014年起，烏克蘭東部頓巴斯地區的平民成了武裝衝突中的受害者。攝：Valery Melnikov<br />\n<br />\n人物特寫<br />\n<br />\n單幅一等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/9321733b557744b59df107e828b1fe1e.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/930/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F9321733b557744b59df107e828b1fe1e.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F930%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=2ea27215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n五歲的Maha跟她的家人一起從伊拉克摩蘇爾郊外的Hawija村逃走。 Maha的媽媽指他們一家因缺乏食物的情況下，及對伊斯蘭國感到恐懼而迫使他們離開家園。攝：Magnus Wennman<br />\n<br />\n體育<br />\n<br />\n圖輯三等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/ad2349956e0a43299b6a41c91a81c5b8.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2Fad2349956e0a43299b6a41c91a81c5b8.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=ae47188f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來自加拿大的Lindsay Hilton，出世時沒有手和腳，卻能舉100磅的槓鈴。攝：Darren Calabrese<br />\n<br />\n焦點新聞<br />\n<br />\n單幅一等獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/0a5faf52a3d34198ad4b1e1992a52428.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F0a5faf52a3d34198ad4b1e1992a52428.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=523d1adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在巴基斯坦奎達發生炸彈爆炸後，一名律師正幫助受傷的同事。當時炸彈在民用醫院外爆炸，期間正有一群律師和記者正聚集在一起哀悼一名被暗殺的高級律師Bilal Anwar Kasi，最後共有七十人死亡。攝：Jamal Taraqai<br />\n<br />\n[img]圖輯三等獎<br />\n<a href=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/59f861526d0c4517b900f56f38577693.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F59f861526d0c4517b900f56f38577693.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=b72008d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/59f861526d0c4517b900f56f38577693.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg[/img]</a><br />\n厄立特里亞移民擁擠在一艘大型木船，木船共載了約540名男子，婦女和兒童，準備經地中海到其他安全地方。攝：Mathieu Willcocks<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20170215-photo-worldpress2017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20170215-photo-worldpress2017%2F&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c4a8ae66\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20170215-photo-worldpress2017/</a>"},{"pid":"4d2b9c0c0ee723ca215d44bb53fdddaf49f17366","tid":123403,"uid":73371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:12:16.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827df35c807f46c3281d3fc7491f4c19cc6b8ba9","tid":123403,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:28:24.000Z","msg":"好多都係流血死人既相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c0fb6a798de42ceb02a39c530b2a5ec87e5dea","tid":123403,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:52:43.000Z","msg":"有啲攝影師真係長期係戰場影相？<br />\n咁癲既"},{"pid":"3d81e728ad5f1c0de9716ac3bbec0e26f2bd8e3a","tid":123403,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:09:21.000Z","msg":"救恩島個張係咪老吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我search返英文報導只係話要結婚先可以入東正教社區之類 ，救恩島乜乜係得大陸網同端傳媒報"},{"pid":"e32f771e64f9c9b5997e901a265b6ab9b4434e61","tid":123403,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"圖輯淨係擺一張出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bd84b595017fa4af3b0ca8cbdcdc5e9ad7ad30","tid":123403,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖輯淨係擺一張出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  樓主可唔可以出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725dddedd94d4ff9ecd0fd1ea5f1f384a7b6a846","tid":123403,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:40:57.000Z","msg":"The last one<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2017/02/59f861526d0c4517b900f56f38577693.jpg?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/720/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F59f861526d0c4517b900f56f38577693.jpg%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F720%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=cb6cc757&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3c6e73c03519069e36c6290c2d22c76c5f4de68","tid":123403,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>圖輯淨係擺一張出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  樓主可唔可以出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldpressphoto.org/collection/photo/2017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldpressphoto.org%2Fcollection%2Fphoto%2F2017&